name: Camera Collection
description:
Photography by Jim Golden. Limited Edition of 200; artist signature on back.

Gallery quality, professionally printed image using archival pigment inks on Hahnemuhle Photo Rag paper with a manufacturer’s archival rating of 35+ years.

16" x 20" image on 17" x 21" sheet
24" x 20" image on 25" x 21" sheet

Each print is custom printed and checked for quality by a master printer. Please allow 3-5 business days for your order to be printed. All packages shipped UPS ground out of Portland, Oregon. Shipment tracking will be emailed.

Store business hours are Mon-Thur, 9am-4pm PST. If you order outside of these hours we will process your order on the next business day.
